                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The job of an aquabus maintenance worker isn't easy. When they're not already fixing something, they're constantly on edge, waiting for news of something else that's gone wrong to arrive any minute... It's at times like these that focusing on a few rounds of Genius Invokation TCG helps take their minds off it all.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: When the battle begins, all characters on both sides gain 1 Energy. Each Round, 1 Piercing DMG will be dealt to all of the characters of the first player to declare the end of their Round.",
